enceweb.co.za/land/land-land/ukraines-autokraz-partners-with-nigerias-proforce/</ref>\n| Some locally manufactured.<ref>https://www.defenceweb.co.za/land/land-land/ukraines-autokraz-partners-with-nigerias-proforce/</ref>\n|}\n\n===Engineering Vehicles===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Name\n! style=\"width:15%;\"| Photo\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Type\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Country of Origin\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|In Service\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Notes\n|-\n| [[BOZENA 5]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.naij.com/1077090-nigerian-army-acquires-sophisticated-military-equipment-fight-boko-haram-pho.html|title=Nigerian army acquires more sophisticated equipment to fight Boko Haram (photos)|date=10 December 2016|website=Naij.com}}</ref>\n|\n| Unmanned ground vehicle\n| {{flagu|Slovakia}}\n|\n| clearance of all conventional antipersonnel and antitank land mines and for IED removal assistance.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bozena.eu/general-b5/|title=BOZENA 5 - medium demining system - Bo\u017eena|website=Bozena.eu}}</ref>\n|-\n|Vickers AVLB<ref name=\":1\">{{Cite book|title=Jane's Armour and Artillery 2003\u20132004}}</ref>\n|\n|Armored Bridge-layer\n|United Kingdom\n|26 (status unknown)\n|\n|-\n|Vickers ARV<ref name=\":1\" />\n|\n|Armored Recovery Vehicle\n|United Kingdom\n|12 (Status unknown)\n|\n|}\n\n===Utility Vehicle===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Name\n! style=\"width:15%;\"| Photo\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Type\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Country of Origin\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|In Service\n! style=\"text-align: left;\"|Notes\n|-\n| [[Pinzgauer High-Mobility All-Terrain Vehicle|Pinzgauer]]<ref name=\"Haflinger\">{{cite web|url=http://tdc.haflinger-4wd.com/countries/nigeria.php|title=Steyr Puch Haflinger TDC - Nigeria|author=Constantin Kiesling|website=Tdc.haflinger-4wd.com|accessdate=15 February 2015}}</ref>\n| [[File:Pinzgauer 710-IMG 4935-40.jpg|170px]]\n| High-Mobil